# Production Monitoring Stack: Prometheus & Grafana on Kubernetes

## 📋 Project Overview

Deployed a comprehensive, production-grade observability platform for Kubernetes clusters using Prometheus for metrics collection, Grafana for visualization, and ELK Stack for log aggregation. This solution provides real-time monitoring, alerting, and troubleshooting capabilities across microservices infrastructure.

## 🎯 Business Challenge

**Client:** Fast-growing SaaS company running 50+ microservices on Kubernetes

**Problems:**
- **No visibility** into application performance or infrastructure health
- **Reactive incident management** - problems discovered by customers first
- **Long MTTR** (Mean Time To Resolution) - average 4+ hours to diagnose issues
- **Resource waste** - no capacity planning data, leading to over-provisioning
- **Compliance gaps** - no audit logs or performance metrics for SLA reporting

**Impact:**
- Frequent production outages (2-3 per week)
- Customer complaints about performance
- Engineering team spending 60% time firefighting
- $50k/month in wasted cloud resources
- Inability to meet SLA commitments

